    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including deep scratches, several noticeable dents, and areas of advancing rust. Mechanically, the car requires immediate professional attention as it suffers from a rough-running engine and a transmission that struggles to shift properly. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest significant time and resources to return this vehicle to a roadworthy state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
